data.description: Step into your own backyard sanctuary: a captivating 1,100+ sq ft pool home awaits on a sprawling 1/4+ acre in sunny Inverness, FL. Imagine lazy afternoons by the sparkling pool, pets roaming in the secure fenced yard, and afternoons tinkering in your very own workshop. This charming retreat boasts 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, a one-car garage, and bonus covered parking - perfect for your boat or weekend adventures! Have peace of mind with a recent inspection. New water heater was just installed in February 2024. NEW ROOF will be installed prior to closing along with a new septic drain field. Stroll hand-in-hand to nearby shops, indulging in the quaint, small-town charm of Inverness. Don't miss your chance to claim this piece of paradise - schedule a showing today and unlock your own hidden oasis!
